sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>IncidentListPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>IncidentDetailView
    participant SER as UpdateIncidentSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Select incident, change status dropdown
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/incidents/{id}/ {status: "in_progress"}
    API->>DB: Incident.objects.get(pk=id)
    DB-->>API: Incident instance
    API->>SER: UpdateIncidentSerializer.validate(data)
    SER-->>API: Validated status change
    API->>DB: incident.status = "in_progress"
    API->>DB: incident.save()
    DB-->>API: Updated
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {incident with new status}
    FE-->>U: Status badge updated
